I just -- we're going to have to do things so we can see each other. We never see each other....What do you mean?But -- as soon as we're done with the tour we go back and record, and then we go back on tour.We tour so we can make the record, and then we go back on tour to sell the record....What does that mean?What did you think I was going to do?You didn't think we'd be successful.Yeah, feasibly -- I could be on the road for years with just this record.I don't know how that matters.Do you like the music I'm playing?Yeah, well, I --What are you doing?
